  <description type="morphology">Shrubs not compact, 0.2–0.6(–0.8) m; twig nodes mostly 1+ cm apart.  Leaf blades lanceolate, 2–4 cm, 2.5–4 times as long as wide.  Flowers: calyx light pink, 7–10 mm diam.; corolla rose-purple, 15–20 mm diam.</description>
